@startuml
participant TestCase
participant Calculator
participant "Python Runtime" as Runtime

TestCase -> Calculator : create instance
activate Calculator

TestCase -> Calculator : divide(10, 0)
activate Calculator

Calculator -> Runtime : evaluate 10 / 0
activate Runtime
Runtime --> Calculator : raise ZeroDivisionError
deactivate Runtime

Calculator --> TestCase : ZeroDivisionError propagates
deactivate Calculator

TestCase -> TestCase : assertRaises(ZeroDivisionError) passes
deactivate Calculator

@enduml
